# Phase - UI/UX Rebranding & Design System Modernization
## SOC Compliance Portal
### Version: UI Refresh 1.0

---

# Objective

Act as a **Principal UI/UX Architect**, **Senior Frontend Architect**, **React.js Expert**, and **Enterprise Product Designer**.

Before making any UI changes:

- Analyze the complete React project.
- Understand every screen.
- Understand all existing business functionality.
- Understand component hierarchy.
- Understand routing.
- Understand naming conventions.
- Understand existing design system.
- Understand existing backend integrations.

The objective is **NOT** to rewrite the application.

The objective is to redesign the UI professionally without breaking even a single existing functionality.

---

# Mandatory Rule

**DO NOT BREAK ANY EXISTING FUNCTIONALITY.**

All backend APIs,
all business logic,
all validations,
all workflows,
all role-based permissions,
all data loading,
all report generation,
all Review Commits functionality,
all Release Readiness functionality,
all Generate Report functionality,
all Settings functionality,
all authentication,
must continue working exactly as today.

Only improve UI/UX.

